ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would tell them to take this class so they could get feedback on their NSF proposals and other writing projects.

I would recommend the course on the condition that the student has writing to complete. I found this class most helpful while working on the nsf grand application and feel that I could have benefitted from it more if I had more writing to discuss.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: These skills are necessary for anyone in this field, and the chance to get feedback and develop these skills further is always a good thing.
